      </p>

      <p>
        When booking your appointment, let us know about any elevator
        reservations, parking instructions, entry procedures, or service-hour
        restrictions. We plan the appointment carefully so that the repair can
        be completed with minimal disruption to your residence and building.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Careful Repair for Historic and Hillside Hollywood Homes</h3>

      <p>
        Hollywood also includes historic homes and hillside residences where
        appliance access can require additional care. Properties near Franklin
        Avenue and the residential streets leading toward the hills may include
