      </p>

      <p>
        Whether your appliance is installed inside a restored residence, a
        custom hillside home, or a contemporary remodeled kitchen, our goal is
        to provide careful service while protecting the character and finishes
        of the property.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Your Home Deserves More Than a Quick Fix</h3>

      <p>
        Your luxury appliances were selected for their performance,
        craftsmanship, and design. At <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI</strong>, we deliver a
        repair experience that reflects those same values—with skill,
        discretion, and careful service from start to finish.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>📞 Schedule Your Luxury Appliance Repair in Hollywood Today</h3>

      <p>
        Do not wait for a small appliance issue to become a major disruption.
        <br />
        Call <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> or book online
        now to schedule expert service in Hollywood, Los Angeles.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>
          Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI — Because Hollywood Homes Deserve World-Class Repair.
        </strong>
      </p>
    </section>

